data.description: Welcome to this flawless and fully renovated condo in highly desired Rainbow Glen community. No expense was spared in this gorgeous home.  Remodeled kitchen, recessed lighting, all new luxury vinyl flooring throughout, freshly painted, and offering 4 bedrooms! Upstairs loft was converted into a sizable 4th bedroom with its own closet. Unique top floor with high, two story vaulted ceilings.  A tucked away primary bedroom with an en suite bath, walk-in shower & walk-in closet. Private balcony w/ storage closet, that over looks community walking path, nearby pool, and neighborhood. Privately owned single car garage below. Enjoy walks around the community, amenities such as 2 different pools & tennis courts, and convenient access to all sorts of shopping & restaurants. If you are looking for a turnkey, beautiful home with 4 bedrooms, and a high quality of life, look no further. Hurry, this is the home you have been waiting for!
